## 16. Summary of Data Practices

| Data Type | Collection | Use | Retention | Sharing |
|-----------|-----------|-----|-----------|---------|
| Name | Direct input | Personalization, app functionality | Until deleted | Not shared |
| Gender | Direct input | Personalization | Until deleted | Not shared |
| Affirmations | User-created & AI-generated | Display, personalization | Until deleted | Not shared |
| Photos | User uploaded | Background images, personalization | Until deleted | Not shared |
| User ID | Automatic (Supabase) | Account management | Until deleted | Internal only |
| Device ID | Automatic | Subscription management (Superwall) | Retained by Superwall | Superwall only |
| Onboarding Data | Direct input | Personalization | Until deleted | Not shared |
| App Settings | Automatic | Functionality | Until deleted | Not shared |

---

**Your privacy is important to us. Thank you for trusting It Girl: Affirmations.**

